name: RestaurantFinder
0:
”Alexa, open restaurant finder”
”find good Italian restaurants in Boise”
”find great Chinese restaurants in Seattle”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: restaurant finder
des: Find restaurants in a location based on the type of cuisine, or filter the restaurants by price or by Yelp rating. Restaurant details including the address and phone number read to you directly through your Alexa-enabled device with additional information displayed in the companion Alexa application.
